      • execute

        default void execute​(Shell shell,
                     InputStream in,
                     PrintStream out,
                     PrintStream err,
                     String line0,
                     String code)
              throws Exception
        Entry-point method. Executed in the Shell. Default implementation sends to the execute(NotebookContext,String,String) method in the JShell instance.
        Parameters:
        shell - The Shell.
        in - The in InputStream.
        out - The out PrintStream.
        err - The err PrintStream.
        line0 - The initial magic line.
        code - The remainder of the cell.
        Throws:
        Exception

      • isCellMagic

        static boolean isCellMagic​(String code)
        Method to determine if the code is cell magic (starts with '%%').
        Parameters:
        code - The code to test.
        Returns:
        true if cell magic; false otherwise.

      • getCellMagicCommand

        static String[] getCellMagicCommand​(String code)
        Method to parse a cell magic command. The code must start with "%%". "#" to the EOL is a comment. The command is either a word or a single punctuation character. Words may be quoted with double quotes.
        Parameters:
        code - The code to parse.
        Returns:
        The array of command arguments.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - If the magic line can't be parsed.

      • sendTo

        static void sendTo​(Shell shell,
                   String name,
                   String line0,
                   String code)
            throws Exception
        Static method to send a request to be executed in the JShell instance. The sendTo(Shell,String,String,String) method packs the arguments and creates a receive(String,NotebookContext,String,String) expression which is evaluated in the JShell.
        Parameters:
        shell - The Shell.
        name - The magic name.
        line0 - The initial magic line.
        code - The remainder of the cell.
        Throws:
        Exception
